reviewText: These are great movies of independence and learning yourself.....Both are great for young girls to watch....Great movies for coming of age young ladies
Ellen Page in her best performance yet. The cast of caracters in over the top and the story line well done. Both movies are put together in a fashion you will want to watch over and over!!
You only get Disc 1 for Whip It, so you won't get the featurettes that were on the original release.
Excellent movies for the price. Can't beat it
Ellen Page fan. Michael Cera fan. Indie fan.

Had never seen Whip It, but like Ellen Page so I thought - why not? It was a darling movie! And of course, Juno is what garnered Ellen praise to begin with! So this is a keeper with both movies packaged together. Great value.
